::Shredder/Ramulus::

Shredder grins, seeing Rattrap get hit by one of his shots. He looks at the 
door that the rat ran into, landing and walking forward to open it.

Shredder flies forward into the door as a shot hits him.

"Do you have a good reason to be here?" Ramulus asks, walking up, gun aimed 
at Shredder.

Shredder growls, firing at Ramulus and launching himself into the air.
